summary: This is a download of file called \"bat master\" that makes you level 81 and skills 100
descriptionHtml:
This is a .txt file that you place in your skyrim files.

How-to
_________________

1. download file

2. place in skyrim files
Ex FOR ME...
C:\\Program Files (x86)\\The Elder Scrolls V Skyrim
       ***You may have a different place****

3. start up skyrim and what ever player you want ranked up all the way.

4. hit this key \" ` \" or \" ~ \" next to the 1 or !. This will open console command.

5. Type       bat master  

make sure you put the space between bat and master.

6. exit console command

7. Done
